description:
Spark connection, laughter, and intimacy with Loverzz, the all-in-one app for couples.

Whether you are in a long-distance relationship, newlyweds, or dating, Loverzz helps you grow closer through daily games, home screen widgets, and deep conversations.

Discover what your partner really thinks. One partner answers, the other guesses. Match answers to score points, unlock relationship insights, and ignite meaningful conversations.

DRAWING & WIDGETS
Send love notes directly to your partner's Home Screen. Use our drawing tools to sketch cute doodles or send photo widgets to keep your presence felt, no matter the distance. It is the perfect way to stay connected throughout the day without saying a word.

DAILY QUESTIONS & QUIZZES
From Future Dreams to Intimacy, explore over 13 categories designed to spark conversation. You answer honestly, your partner guesses your answer to see who knows who best. It turns serious relationship building into a fun, low-pressure game.

RELATIONSHIP INSIGHTS
Track your connection across 6 key dimensions: Vision, Intimacy, Adventure, Life Habits, Social Dynamics, and Crisis Management. Watch your understanding grow with visual progress tracking and compatibility scores.

PERFECT FOR LONG DISTANCE
Bridge the gap with digital interactions. The combination of real-time quizzes and Home Screen widgets makes Loverzz the ultimate tool for long-distance couples to stay synced and close, even when miles apart.

13 CONVERSATION CATEGORIES
Avoid running out of things to say. Our card packs range from fun to profound, including Future Dreams, Relationship Growth, Social Situations, Travel Adventures, Family, Career, and Intimacy.

WHY CHOOSE LOVERZZ
- Daily couples questions to build connection rituals
- Drawing and photo widgets for your Home Screen
- Deep conversation starters mixed with fun games
- Designed specifically for couples who want to grow closer

Join thousands of couples making Loverzz their daily habit. Because truly knowing your partner is the ultimate relationship goal.

Download Loverzz now and start your journey to a deeper connection.

Alipay is a leading open platform for payments and digital services in China.

Users with a Chinese ID and bank account can use Alipay to make payments online and in person at various merchants outside of China as they travel for leisure, business, or study. 

Foreign visitors to China can connect their credit card to take advantage of Alipay’s widespread acceptance by tens of millions of merchants across the country. Alipay is not designed or intended for use by foreign users in their home country or anywhere outside of China.

Muslim: Quran, Athan & Qibla is your comprehensive Islamic companion, designed to support your daily spiritual journey. With essential features like accurate prayer time reminders, Azkar collection, and Qibla direction, it helps strengthen your faith and manage your daily worship seamlessly.

Key Features:

* Accurate Prayer Times: Never miss a prayer again! Get precise notifications for all Salah times (Fajr, Dhuhr, Asr, Maghrib, Isha) based on your location.
* Azkar & Duas: Immerse yourself in spiritual invocations with a curated collection of Azkar and Duas, perfect for morning, evening, and every moment in between. Strengthen your connection with Allah through heartfelt invocations.
* Tasbih Counter: Elevate your Dhikr practice with the built-in Tasbih Counter. This feature includes an electronic tasbih and prayer bead counter to help you track your count while reciting your prayer or Dua.
* Qibla Direction: Find the Qibla direction accurately, no matter where you are. The integrated Qibla compass ensures precise alignment for your prayers.
* Quran Access: Read and reflect on the Holy Quran directly within the app. The clear and user-friendly interface allows for easy navigation between chapters and verses, supporting your daily recitation goals.
* Prayer Reminders: Never miss a prayer with customizable reminders that fit your routine. Whether it's a gentle nudge for Fajr or a midday reminder for Dhuhr, you'll stay connected to your worship schedule.

Muslim: Quran, Athan & Qibla is designed to be your trusted spiritual companion, integrating faith seamlessly into your daily routine. Whether you're managing prayer times, reflecting on Quranic verses, or seeking solace in Azkar and Duas, this app supports your spiritual growth and devotion.

Download now and experience the convenience, guidance, and fulfillment of having a complete Islamic companion right at your fingertips. Stay connected to your faith, no matter where life takes you.

Welcome to Supreme King: Your Ultimate Local Impact App

Supreme King is your go-to platform for transforming everyday tasks into opportunities for meaningful change in your community. With Supreme King, you're not just completing tasks; you're reigning supreme as a local leader, making a lasting impact one task at a time.

Here's what Supreme King has to offer:

Discover Local Tasks: Explore a wide range of tasks posted by individuals, businesses, and organizations in your area. Whether it's checking supermarket shelves, delivering groceries, or running errands for your neighbors, there's a task suited to your skills and interests.

Complete Tasks with Purpose: When you accept a task on Supreme King, you're embracing a chance to make a difference. Follow the task instructions diligently and complete it with pride, knowing that your efforts are directly contributing to positive change in your community.

Donate Your Earnings: At Supreme King, we believe in the power of giving back. Instead of keeping the earnings from your completed tasks, choose to donate them to local charities and nonprofit organizations through the app. Your contributions support crucial community initiatives, such as feeding the hungry, supporting education, and promoting environmental sustainability.

Track Your Impact: Keep track of your completed tasks and the impact you've made over time with Supreme King's intuitive tracking features. Watch as your small actions add up to make a big difference in your community, and celebrate your role as a true local leader.

Why Choose Supreme King?

Empowerment: Supreme King empowers you to reign supreme as a force for good in your community. With every task completed and donation made, you're leading by example and inspiring others to join the movement.

Community Collaboration: Join forces with fellow Supreme Kings and Queens who share your passion for making a difference. Connect, collaborate, and amplify your impact together, creating a ripple effect of positive change across your community.

Transparency: We believe in transparency and accountability every step of the way. With Supreme King, you'll have full visibility into where your donations go and how they're making a difference in your community. Your trust is our top priority.

Ease of Use: Supreme King is designed to be user-friendly and accessible to all. Whether you're a seasoned volunteer or new to community service, our app makes it easy to get involved and start making a difference right away.

Ready to seize your throne as a local hero? Download Supreme King today and embark on your journey to making a lasting impact in your community. Together, we can build a brighter future for all.

Sports live in the moments. That NBA buzzer-beater. The NFL touchdown in overtime. The soccer goal in the 90th minute. The quiz question only true fans get right. Kuki brings it all together.

Watch any match highlight, completely free. A quick ad unlocks the action. No subscriptions splitting your wallet. No paywalls blocking the best moments. Just pure sports, instantly accessible.

Live scores pulse through the app the second they happen. Your teams score, you know. Games start, you're ready. Final whistles blow, you're already celebrating or analyzing what went wrong. Real-time means real-time.

Notifications keep you connected to every moment. Kickoff alerts fifteen minutes before games start. Instant score notifications the second they happen. Final score updates when time expires. Highlight availability alerts when videos are ready. Customize everything - choose which teams, which events, which times. Your phone becomes your personal sports command center.

Stay informed with curated sports news. NBA trades. NFL signings. Soccer transfers. Injury updates. Game previews. Post-game analysis. Everything that matters across all sports. News that keeps you ahead of the conversation.

Quizzes turn watching into competing. Daily sports trivia spanning NBA, NFL, and soccer. Global leaderboards. Winning streaks that multiply your points. Suddenly you're not just following sports - you're proving you know them better than thousands of other fans.

The app feels alive. Dark theme that's easy on the eyes. Colors that shift with your teams. Animations that flow. Everything loads instantly. Nothing feels clunky or slow. Sports at the speed they actually happen.

One tap adds games to your calendar with automatic reminders. Search finds anything in milliseconds. Team profiles run deep. Game stats tell the full story. Lineups, formations, matchups - it's all there.

Highlights always show up. Our system finds them when others give up. Official sources first. Alternative platforms next. Something always plays. Empty screens don't exist here.

NBA. NFL. Soccer. Every league. Every team. Every game that matters. The whole sports world in your pocket.

Download Kuki and feel the difference.

Your multi-sport companion for live scores, fixtures, highlights, standings, and team insights—all in a fast, neon-clean iOS experience. Pick your favorite sports and leagues; our app personalizes the home feed, notifications, and suggestions around what you love.

Why It Stands Out

Multi-Sport, One Flow: Easily switch between football, basketball, American football, baseball, and more—all organized the same, so you never relearn the app.

Match-Day Engine: From fixtures to live stats, line-ups, timelines, and highlights, the app keeps the essential match details together and easy to swipe.

Smart Highlights: Surfaces official match videos and reputable publisher highlights when available; plays inline for a seamless experience.

Built for Personalization: Onboarding captures your favorite leagues and teams; the app tailors scores, alerts, and suggestions to you.

Fast, Neon-Clean UI: SwiftUI interface with a dark-first design, crisp visuals, and smooth interactions.

Core Features

Live & Upcoming: Real-time scores and upcoming fixtures, prioritized for your favorites.

Match Centre: Overview, timeline, stats, line-ups, and media—organized in clear tabs.

Highlights Hub: Match highlights and media with transparent source context.

News You’ll Care About: Curated football news headlines from recognized outlets; team-focused updates when you follow clubs.

Powerful Search: Quickly find teams, players, and events; helpful suggestions for popular clubs and stars.

Favorites & Alerts: Follow leagues and teams; granular notifications for match start, live updates, and final results.

Calendar Sync: Add fixtures to your iOS Calendar with one tap, including reminders.

Standings & Teams: League tables, squads, player profiles, and form at a glance.

Privacy & Principles

No Account Required: Your favorites, alerts, and preferences stay on your device.

Transparent Sources: Uses public sports APIs, official channels, and reputable publishers. The app does not host copyrighted streams or attempt to bypass DRM.

Independent App: Not affiliated with or endorsed by leagues, teams, or rights holders.

Availability Notes

Coverage and highlight availability can vary by sport, league, region, and publisher rights.

Make every match day shine—across your favorite sports.
Turn on your leagues, set your alerts, and let Sport Live bring live scores, highlights, and the details that matter into one fast, focused experience.

UPGRADE TO TINDER PLATINUM
Get most of Tinder’s premium features: join Tinder Platinum™ to get your likes prioritised with potential matches, send them a compliment before matching and more.
